item.title: [317] How do i change home area::?**SOLVED
item.dc:creator: @WestSideMass WestSideMass
item.description:
@WestSideMass wrote:

Go to your home area and type in ::mypos. It will tell you the coordinates.
After that, go into Client.Java and search for those coordinates.
Delete those, and put in your coordinates.
